    <section id="id3845399">
      <title>LEARNING OUTCOME 3: READING AND VIEWING</title>
      <para id="id3938277">The learner will be able to read and view for information and enjoyment, and to respond critically to the aesthetic, cultural and emotional values in texts.</para>
      <section id="id4202836">
        <title>Assessment Standard</title>
        <para id="id3753093">We know this when the learner:</para>
        <para id="id3534331">3.3 reads for information:</para>
