        <para id="id4297426">3.5 reads for pleasure and information:</para>
        <para id="id4340730">3.5.1 reads fiction and non-fiction books at an appropriate reading and language level;</para>
        <para id="id3787970">3.5.3 reads and solves puzzles;</para>
